# Personal, machine-specific Claude Code settings (not shared)
.claude/settings.local.json

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Personal/working docs — keep only the shareable requirements spec
docs/Project Plan.md
docs/progress-notes.md
docs/requirements.old.md
docs/build-tasks.md

# Local-only docs — anything under docs/local/ stays on this machine
docs/local/

# Superpowers brainstorm scratch/state — machine-specific working files
.superpowers/

# Personal household config — keep only the .example templates, ignore real filled-in files
config/*.md
!config/*.example.md

# Personal recipes — keep only the schema template + the shared example recipes; ignore the rest
recipes/*.md
!recipes/_template.md
!recipes/beef-taco-bowls.md
!recipes/sheet-pan-chicken-fajitas.md
